<#
.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script Ensure Compliance for AllowDomainPINLogon

.NOTES
    Author          : Felix
    LinkedIn        : linkedin.com/in/somuadina-amadi-599348333/
    GitHub          : github.com/felix2470/
    Date Created    : 4/22/2025
